{"id": "1392444966508433418", "channel_id": "1392444812946313226", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "V2.2.3.2 Online Maintenance Announcement\n\nDear Keeper,\nThe Mythag Administration Office will conduct campus facility maintenance on Julyj 9 at 18:00. You will be notified once the update is complete and you can re-enter the game. As an apology for any inconvenience caused by the update, we will provide a supply package. Wishing everyone a successful investigation!\n\n\n[Compensation]\nOnline Maintenance Compensation: Silver*50\n\n\n[Claim Conditions]\nThe claiming time ends on July 14, 2025 at 23:59. Please remember to go to your mailbox in time to claim the supply materials.\n\n[Update Content]\n1. Version Cycle Adjustment\n● Due to our desire to find more suitable voice actors for the upcoming new Awakened bodies and re-record related content, Version 2.3.0 will be delayed by at least 7 days (until July 21).\n    ○ We sincerely apologize for any inconvenience caused to Keepers by the above changes. During the delay period, we will provide 500 Silver Cores daily to Keepers as an apology.\n    ○ The time to claim the Silver Core compensation ends before the V2.3.0 version update.\n    ○ A future version will be shortened in duration to offset the impact of this version cycle change, and we will announce this in advance in that version's release notes.\n● Gameplay Event \"The Great Conquest\"\n    ○ The end date of the gameplay event \"The Great Conquest\" is now adjusted to 9:00 on July 21.\n    ○ Increased the number of items available in \"Offering Tribute.\"\n    ○ The end time of the \"Restaurant Special\" series limited-time gift boxes has been adjusted to 9:00 on July 21.", "timestamp": "2025-07-09T09:59:10.392000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id":