{"id": "1392445054945198173", "channel_id": "1392444812946313226", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "● [Special Academy Event: Episode 19]\n    ○ This academy event’s duration has been extended until 9:00 on July 21!\n    ○ Episode 19 \"Academy Gift\"\n        ■ Event duration extended to 9:00 on July 21.\n        ■ Added rewards for Days 15 through 21.\n    ○ The end times for Episode 19 \"Mission Records\" and Season 19 \"The Great Conquest\" have been adjusted to 9:00 on July 21.\n● [Cranial Court Elegy - Limited Journey]\n    ○ The purchase deadline for \"Cranial Court Elegy - Limited Journey\" has been adjusted to 9:00 on August 18.\n    ○ The purchase deadline for exclusive limited-time rewards has been adjusted to 9:00 on July 21.\n    ○ The claimable time for Packages 3-8 of \"Cranial Court Elegy - Limited Journey\" has been postponed by 7 days accordingly.\n● [Event Re-release: Meltdown·Dore]\n    ○ Character Event Awakening: \"Absolute Foreseer\" end time has been extended to 9:00 on July 21.\n    ○ Fatewheel Event Awakening: \"Void Projection\" end time has been extended to 9:00 on July 21.\n    ○ Trial Event \"Rotten Brain\": End time has been extended to 9:00 on July 21.", "timestamp": "2025-07-09T09:59:31.477000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1392444812946313226", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.2.3.2 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
